name: Pixel Girlfriend #50
description:
Pixel Girlfriends are a collection of handmade and generative babes. This one is yours!
[Thank You edition]
Thank you to everyone who have been supporting this collection since the beginning. We reach the first 50 pieces of this collection, and I honestly could not have done this without your help.
Thank you for the purchase, your bids, your RT. Thank you for enjoying my art.
I have never been so rewarding for my artwork, never have I experienced such love and support towards my effort. Never have I felt motivated and inspired to keep going.
I am grateful with all my heart.
-𝘛𝘩𝘢𝘯𝘬 𝘠𝘰𝘶 ♥
